<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
   <meta charset="UTF-8" />
   <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
   <title>마이페이지 상세</title>
   <style>
      body {
         font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
         margin: 0;
         padding: 0;
         background-color: #f0f0f0;
      }

      /* 헤더바 */
      .header {
         display: flex;
         justify-content: space-between;
         align-items: center;
         padding: 10px;
         background-color: #fff;
      }

      .navbar {
         display: flex;
         width: 100%;
         justify-content: space-between;
      }

      .menu-icon,
      .settings-icon {
         cursor: pointer;
      }

      .logo {
         text-align: center;
      }

      /* 헤더바 */

      .profile-header {
         display: flex;
         align-items: center;
         padding: 20px;
         background-color: #fff;
      }

      .profile-photo {
         width: 70px;
         height: 70px;
         border-radius: 50%;
         background: url('your-profile-photo-url.jpg') no-repeat center center;
         background-size: cover;
         margin-right: 10px;
      }

      .profile-info {
         flex-grow: 1;
      }

      .profile-name {
         font-weight: bold;
      }

      .profile-school {
         color: #666;
      }

      .edit-button {
         background-color: #007bff;
         color: white;
         padding: 5px 10px;
         border: none;
         cursor: pointer;
      }

      .self-introduction {
         padding: 20px;
         background-color: #fff;
         margin-top: 10px;
      }
   </style>
</head>

<body>
   <%- include('../component/header')%>
      <div class="profile-header">
         <img class="profile-photo"
            src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"
            alt="">
         <div class="profile-info">
            <div class="profile-name">홍길동</div>
            <div class="profile-school">홍길동고등학교</div>
            <button class="edit-button">쪽지보내기</button>
         </div>
      </div>

      <div class="self-introduction">
         <p>자기소개</p>
         안녕하세요. 홍길동 고등학교 2학년입니다.
      </div>


</body>

</html>